50|$|Corned {{beef and}} pastrami on rye may be {{prepared}} using rye bread, pastrami, corned beef, cole slaw, and Russian dressing. Preparation involves placing both meats on a <b>slice</b> <b>of</b> rye <b>bread</b> and topping it with coleslaw. Russian dressing may {{be added to}} the top <b>slice</b> <b>of</b> <b>bread.</b>|$|R
