5000|$|A {{peanut butter}} and jelly sandwich, or PB&J, {{includes}} one or more layers of {{peanut butter and}} one or more layers of either jelly or jam on bread. Sometimes the sandwich is eaten open-faced or with one <b>slice</b> <b>of</b> <b>bread</b> folded over (effectively a [...] "half sandwich"). If the peanut butter is not spread on each <b>slice</b> <b>of</b> <b>bread,</b> the sandwich will become soggy if it is left too long to sit.|$|R
